data.description:
Presenting an extraordinary opportunity in the heart of Richmond Hill North, Queens â€“ a magnificent 2-family brick residence that embodies comfort and adaptability. Situated on a 20 ft x 90 ft lot, this expansive property boasts a generous 2,210 sqft of living space. This meticulously cared-for home includes a fully finished basement, providing ample room for recreation, storage, or creative endeavors. The first floor welcomes you with three inviting bedrooms, ensuring abundant privacy and personal space. A tastefully designed living room creates a tranquil environment for unwinding, while the adjoining kitchen caters to culinary enthusiasts, offering a delightful focal point for meal preparation and gatherings. Completing the main level is a contemporary bathroom, combining convenience with style.
Ascending to the second floor, you'll find another three bedrooms, accompanied by a charming small room that could serve as a nursery, office, or a delightful reading nook. A second living room provides additional space for relaxation, and a second kitchen equipped with modern amenities caters to your culinary desires. A second stylish bathroom completes this upper level. With an annual tax of just $6,619.12, this property offers the potential for comfortable living and rental income. Whether you're an investor seeking a reliable return or a homeowner looking to generate extra revenue, this home is poised to meet your requirements.
In a neighborhood known for its convenience, this residence offers easy access to local amenities, schools, and transportation options, including the J train and buses to Manhattan, making it an appealing choice for those in search of a well-rounded living experience. Seize this opportunity to own this 2-family treasure in the lively community of Richmond Hill North, Queens. Recent renovations include the basement in 2020, as well as the second-floor kitchen and bathroom. The two hot water heater were replaced in 2020, and the roof was redone 6 years ago.
